results.name: Expansion of eighth root of theta series of D_8 lattice.
link: Vaclav Kotesovec, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500
N. Heninger, E. M. Rains and N. J. A. Sloane, On the Integrality of n-th Roots of Generating Functions, J. Combinatorial Theory, Series A, 113 (2006), 1732-1745.
mathematica: terms = 16; f[q_] = LatticeData["D8", "ThetaSeriesFunction"][-I Log[q]/Pi]; s = Series[f[q]^(1/8), {q, 0, 2 terms}]; CoefficientList[s, q^2][[1 ;; terms]] // Round (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Jul 07 2017 *)
CoefficientList[Series[((EllipticTheta[3, 0, Sqrt[x]]^8 + EllipticTheta[4, 0, Sqrt[x]]^8)/2)^(1/8), {x, 0, 20}], x] (* _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Dec 10 2017 *)
